Description: Matrix chat client (GTK4)
 Tesseract is a cross-platform Matrix/chat client with end-to-end
 encryption, image packs (MSC2545), voice messages (MSC3245), replies,
 message editing, and sticker support.
 .
 This package provides the GTK4 variant and installs
 /usr/bin/tesseract-matrix-gtk; it conflicts with tesseract-matrix.
